cast.overview: Two high school girls are best friends until one dates the other's older brother, who is totally his sister's nemesis.
cast.title: The Edge of Seventeen

details.biography: Blake Alexander Jenner (born August 27, 1992) is an American actor and singer. Jenner won the second season of Oxygen's The Glee Project and, as a result, portrayed Ryder Lynn on the Fox musical comedy-drama series Glee. He has since had starring and supporting roles in Everybody Wants Some!! (2016), The Edge of Seventeen (2016), American Animals (2018), and What/If (2019).
details.name: Blake Jenner
